data.description: Country living, yet close to town! Coveted Boston Harbor area home featuring 2828sf, 3bed, 2.5ba on 3.9acres w/view of Big Fishtrap bay. Grand entry invites you into the light filled space with gorgeous hardwood floors throughout the main floor. You will fall in love with the gourmet kitchen w/7 burner, two oven & dual fuel range, commercial hood vent, pot filler, under cabinet lighting, subway tile backsplash, quartz counters, farm sink, new appliances & WI pantry. Great room concept w/gas fp, & eating area. Main floor also has dining room & office/den. Spacious primary bedroom flooded with light, 5pc bath, WI closet & FP. Upstairs has 2 more bedrooms, full bath, laundry & bonus room. 3car garage w/abundant storage & heat pump. A must see!
